OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of clear intervals and
OL,7,Fshowers, these more frequent over
OL,8,FArgyll in the evening and early night.
OL,9,FDrier later in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fotherwise rather cloudy. Mainly dry
OL,13,Fwith just a few scattered showers.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,16,Fon Saturday with a few showers
OL,17,Fbreaking out. Dry much of Sunday then
OL,18,Frain spreading from northwest later,
OL,19,Flasting into Monday before brightening
OL,20,Fup later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
